{"tid":2449864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"布林肯︰與受制裁的香港官員進行交易的外國金融機構 會受到美國制裁。","createTime":"2021-03-17T03:52:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T00:00:54.000Z","uid":13663,"like":162,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"077da749fc34b2eba30e2be02465524c643a44f7","tid":2449864,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:52:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n6vwV0u.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn6vwV0u.gif&h=be531786&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6ea71fed499299a95961a907c0219acdef985b44","tid":2449864,"uid":13663,"like":56,"dislike":1,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:54:42.000Z","msg":"美國國務卿布林肯表示，根據《香港自治法案》的最新報告，全國人大在上周通過修過香港選舉制度的決定，單方面破壞香港的選舉制度，報告亦確認24名中國和香港官員的行為削弱香港自治，與相關官員進行重大交易的外國金融機構會受到美國制裁。"},{"pid":"5c4c52e3e7dc22f6f0ae32fe20c85cd41ada0079","tid":2449864,"uid":72034,"like":44,"dislike":22,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:56:08.000Z","msg":"all action , no talk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3c47597f5d25cc5b0a61618905b5e25f5d2b92","tid":2449864,"uid":13663,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:56:48.000Z","msg":"布林肯指人大決定單方面破壞香港選舉制度<br />\n17/3/2021 11:44<br />\n<br />\n        美國國務卿布林肯表示, 根據香港自治法案發表的最新報告, 指全國人大在上星期通過修改香港選舉制度的決定, 單方面破壞香港的選舉制度.<br />\n<br />\n        布林肯說, 報告確認24名中國和香港官員的行為, 削弱香港的自治, 和有關官員進行重大交易的外國金融機構, 會受到美國制裁."},{"pid":"5b48abebfe8dde92a1f464e665344ca7c52bab34","tid":2449864,"uid":156652,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:57:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UCbTpVf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUCbTpVf.gif&h=7208256c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YA0ADfg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYA0ADfg.gif&h=b4c34f1e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7oExFtC.gif\" data-thumbnail-s