前夕，表示根據《香港自治法》去年10月的報告發佈更新內容，批評全國人大「單方面破壞」香港的選舉制度，並點名24名中港官員損害香港自治權。被點名的中港官員早前已在制裁名單上<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院周三更新報告內容，布林肯在聲明指深切關注全國人大在本月11日「單方面破壞」香港選舉制度的決定，認為是進一步破壞了曾向港人承諾的高度自治，亦違反了《中英聯合聲明》。他指報告中點名的包括14名全國人大常委會副委員長、香港國安處及港澳辦的人員等，並表明外資機構如與這些人等有交易，可被美國當局制裁。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210317/RKKL7OVOOVBP7MFRAMZETGIVFU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210317%2FRKKL7OVOOVBP7MFRAMZETGIVFU%2F&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixfhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=fb72d7a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210317%2FRKKL7OVOOVBP7MFRAMZETGIVFU%2F&h=bf264ae1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210317/RKKL7OVOOVBP7MFRAMZETGIVFU/</a>"},{"pid":"7a8e8eb481a2aa4c9113b44469a8bec2f7f4dc61","tid":2449864,"uid":199669,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"6452874a160599df58490e6952174bf6218869a4","tid":2449864,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5d085f4fb1f17c8f9cdb598a3a402df36a366ab","tid":2449864,"uid":24335,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"748b07335119519e54b8def78c927738012f50fa","tid":2449864,"uid":13503,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:59:17.000Z","msg":"今次講到明金融機構即係有銀行當美帝無到<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T04:00:08.000Z","msg":"匯豐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T04:00:48.000Z","msg":"應該係中資銀行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T04:17:26.000Z","msg":"中資醒過你，肯定屈hsbc個類食死貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76b2edf971e4e41a069c42bed7ea148103bc35db","tid":2449864,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T04:17:53.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abf1823f3d